data.description: This wonderful bungalow shines with craftsmanship and style.  You'll love the hardwood floors throughout, original woodwork, paneled doors and 1920's character paired with updates throughout. The beautiful, updated kitchen has subway tile backsplash, granite countertops and plenty of cabinet and counter space. Entertaining made easy with the formal dining room & a stunning built in buffet. The spacious living room has built in bookshelves, a woodburning fireplace & crown moulding. There are 2 nice size bedrooms on the main floor & an updated full bathroom. Head upstairs to the cozy loft/office area & the primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and updated primary bathroom that has a stunning large shower & beautiful tile work throughout. Enjoy the charming front porch on a sunny morning! The backyard has a large deck & gazebo for summer nights spent entertaining with a privacy fence & large newer 2 car garage w/an extra parking pad! The lower level is ready for your finishing touches!
